nt-text\">Drama & Rumit</span>\n            </h1>\n\n            <!-- Subheadline -->\n            <p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-slate-400 mb-10 animate-[fadeInUp_1s_ease-out_0.4s_both]\">\n                Automasi pemasaran, penjualan, dan operasional Anda dalam satu dashboard pintar. Tingkatkan profit tanpa menambah jam kerja.\n            </p>\n\n            <!-- CTA Buttons -->\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 animate-[fadeInUp_1s_ease-out_0.6s_both]\">\n                <button class=\"px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/25 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1\">\n                    Mulai Trial 14 Hari\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-white font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-slate-700 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2\">\n                    <i class=\"ph-fill ph-play-circle text-xl\"></i> Tonton Demo\n                </button>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Hero Image / Dashboard Mockup -->\n            <div class=\"mt-20 relative animate-float\">\n                <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark via-transparent to-transparent z-10 h-full w-full pointer-events-none\"></div>\n                <div class=\"relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20 border border-slate-700/50 max-w-5xl mx-auto group\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"></div>\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2426&q=80\" alt=\"Dashboard App Interface\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-cover opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Social Proof (Logos) -->\n    <section class=\"py-10 border-y border-slate-800/50 bg-slate-900/30\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n            <p class=\"text-center text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-8\">Dipercaya oleh 500+ Startup Inovatif</p>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-8 md:gap-16 opacity-50 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500\">\n                <!-- Logo Placeholders using Text for simplicity, replace with SVGs -->\n                <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><i class=\"ph ph-google-logo\"></i> Google</span>\n                <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><i class=\"ph ph-meta-logo\"></i> Meta</span>\n                <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><i class=\"ph ph-spotify-logo\"></i> Spotify</span>\n                <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><i class=\"ph ph-amazon-logo\"></i> Amazon</span>\n                <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><i class=\"ph ph-stripe-logo\"></i> Stripe</span>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Features Section -->\n    <section id=\"fitur\" class=\"py-24 relative\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n            <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n                <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">Fitur yang Membuat Anda <span class=\"text-primary\">Unggul</span></h2>\n                <p class=\"text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Kami merancang Nexus untuk menghilangkan pekerjaan repetitif, sehingga Anda bisa fokus pada strategi besar.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Feature 1 -->\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 mb-24 reveal\">\n      