nded-lg shadow-lg\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-6\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-secondary mb-4\">\n                        <i class=\"ph-fill ph-lightning text-2xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Automasi Tanpa Coding</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed\">\n                        Hubungkan aplikasi favorit Anda (WhatsApp, Gmail, Trello) dan biarkan Nexus bekerja. Set \"Jika X maka Y\" dalam hitungan detik.\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-3 text-slate-300\">\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check-circle text-green-400\"></i> Drag-and-drop builder</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check-circle text-green-400\"></i> 100+ Template siap pakai</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Stats Section -->\n    <section class=\"py-20 bg-slate-900 border-y border-slate-800\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center\">\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2\">10k+</div>\n                    <div class=\"text-slate-500\">Pengguna Aktif</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2\">$50M</div>\n                    <div class=\"text-slate-500\">Transaksi Diproses</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2\">99.9%</div>\n                    <div class=\"text-slate-500\">Uptime Server</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6\">\n                    <div class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2\">24/7</div>\n                    <div class=\"text-slate-500\">Support Tim</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Testimonials -->\n    <section id=\"testimoni\" class=\"py-24 bg-dark relative overflow-hidden\">\n        <div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10\"></div>\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-16\">Kata Mereka Tentang Nexus</h2>\n            \n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n                <!-- Card 1 -->\n                <div class=\"p-8 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2\">\n                    <div class=\"flex gap-1 text-yellow-400 mb-4\">\n                        <i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-300 mb-6 italic\">\"Saya tidak pernah menyangka automasi bisa semudah ini. Omzet naik 200% dalam 3 bulan pertama pemakaian.\"</p>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n                        <img src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg\" alt=\"User\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-600\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold\">Andi Pratama</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">CEO, Digital Agency</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Card 2 -->\n                <div class=\"p-8 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2\">\n                    <div class=\"flex gap-1 text-yellow-400 mb-4\">\n                        <i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-300 mb-6 italic\">\"Fitur laporannya sangat detail tapi mudah dibaca. Tim marketing saya jadi lebih produktif tanpa harus lembur.\"</p>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n                        <img src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg\" alt=\"User\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-600\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold\">Sarah Wijaya</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Founder, E-commerce</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Card 3 -->\n                <div class=\"p-8 rounded-2xl bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2\">\n                    <div class=\"flex gap-1 text-yellow-400 mb-4\">\n                        <i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star\"></i><i class=\"ph-fill ph-star-half\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-slate-300 mb-6 italic\">\"Supportnya luar biasa cepat. Setiap ada kendala teknis, selalu diselesaikan dalam hitungan menit. Recommended!\"</p>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n                        <img src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/86.jpg\" alt=\"User\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 border-slate-600\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h4 class=\"text-white font-bold\">Budi Santoso</h4>\n                            <p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Owner, Coffee Shop Chain</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Pricing Section -->\n    <section id=\"pricing\" class=\"py-24 bg-slate-900 relative\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n            <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n                <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">Investasi Cerdas untuk Bisnis</h2>\n                <p class=\"text-slate-400\">Pilih paket yang sesuai dengan fase pertumbuhan bisnis Anda.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-8\">\n                \n                <!-- Starter Plan -->\n                <div class=\"w-full max-w-md p-8 bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500 transition-colors\">\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-2\">Starter</h3>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-6\">\n                        <span class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-white\">Rp 199k</span>\n                        <span class=\"text-slate-500\">/bulan</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 mb-8\">Cocok untuk freelancer atau solopreneur yang baru mulai.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"block w-full py-3 px-6 text-center rounded-xl bg-slate-700 text-white font-bold hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors mb-8\">Pilih Starter</a>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check text-primary\"></i> 1 User Admin</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check text-primary\"></i> 5 Projek Aktif</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check text-primary\"></i> Analitik Dasar</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 opacity-50\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-x text-slate-500\"></i> Custom Domain</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Pro Plan (Highlighted) -->\n                <div class=\"w-full max-w-md p-8 bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border-2 border-primary relative shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20 transform scale-105 z-10\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">\n                        Paling Laris\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2\">Professional</h3>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-6\">\n                        <span class=\"text-5xl font-bold text-white\">Rp 499k</span>\n                        <span class=\"text-slate-500\">/bulan</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 mb-8\">Power penuh untuk bisnis yang sedang berkembang pesat.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"block w-full py-3 px-6 text-center rounded-xl bg-primary text-white font-bold hover:bg-indigo-500 transition-colors mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30\">Mulai Trial Gratis</a>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-white text-sm\">\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check-circle text-green-400\"></i> 5 User Admin</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check-circle text-green-400\"></i> Unlimited Projek</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check-circle text-green-400\"></i> Analitik Advanced</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check-circle text-green-400\"></i> Integrasi API</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check-circle text-green-400\"></i> Prioritas Support</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Enterprise Plan -->\n                <div class=\"w-full max-w-md p-8 bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500 transition-colors\">\n                    <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-2\">Enterprise</h3>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-6\">\n                        <span class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-white\">Hubungi</span>\n                        <!-- <span class=\"text-slate-500\">Kami</span> -->\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 mb-8\">Solusi custom untuk perusahaan skala besar dengan kebutuhan khusus.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"block w-full py-3 px-6 text-center rounded-xl bg-slate-700 text-white font-bold hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors mb-8\">Kontak Sales</a>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check text-primary\"></i> Unlimited User</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check text-primary\"></i> Dedicated Server</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check text-primary\"></i> SLA 99.99%</li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><i class=\"ph-fill ph-check text-primary\"></i> Manager Akun Pribadi</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- FAQ S